{"h2f00d8ffged7fg4140g8457gc2cefaeaf217": ["We should make a run for it. ", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "3347ea1f-e8c6-cb99-9980-c3017b3fe2df"], "h2d88acccg0adcg49d3g888dgb3da01ef9583": ["They'd tear us apart. You saw what happened to the others.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "7e9547bc-5e8d-60f3-9f7a-44095036da15"], "hbee6e623g7357g45e2gb8e1g81d51c778cc1": ["That fire won't hold them forever.", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "ca4a55a7-54d0-6d9b-264a-cf58fc38c864"], "h19f8d544g6a09g422agabf1g6719ff8051de": ["I know! But we don't stand a chance out there.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "2d061e61-aba1-de8b-5d99-8e897d0e29f7"], "had3af11egcec2g4ec7g98dcgfdd9a2b3d646": ["Someone must have found the wagon by now.", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "eeec23b0-e890-e34d-6932-91539265d883"], "haf678a5dg02c2g4f5dgac86g4f214c7156e3": ["Maybe.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "4b0b02c5-aef6-f1c0-61ae-fcf7e401420d"], "hbf312929g327fg4ad0gb7f1gbe31894ac3b3": ["So help's on its way?", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "da71ee43-659a-9f62-683f-552387cb2825"], "hf1aa4a54g9ea4g4cc0gb49cgf98451fdba00": ["Only if whoever found the wagon is stupid enough to fight a pack of gnolls.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "face9e3c-7ad8-2e36-4c7d-8f9e67827659"], "h8b24796dge44dg419bg93dfg4da5c7543e4d": ["So, no. I think help's a long way from here.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "9c068cd1-7a94-42de-9506-4e7d56db3e8f"], "hcdd2cb12gdd5eg407eg8cb2g7ad622e78403": ["There must be another way out!", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "91104a2e-fb3c-ed65-e506-2d1fee603f4d"], "hbdd50257g272bg4568gaa39g2d140453eafd": ["There is. Hurl yourself into the chasm back there.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "cf48875e-4ea1-7b9f-5f31-660327f2942f"], "h2d4d299dg6e23g476fga874gded102db861d": ["I'd break my neck!", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "4fa3334c-00ca-8918-599d-9a654eefe892"], "hd0c4b2acge58eg4a2ag9a48g4cd98f23d8be": ["Aye. It'd be quicker than having your guts torn out by them beasts.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "5b95404a-b85d-bc83-6aac-3bd0ea5e4881"], "ha66d1747g4acbg4ebdga128gacaf403819a9": ["Well, lad. It's our lucky day after all.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "daefbc49-e4ad-cd20-036d-a7dc58b87f09"], "h8f1bca75g638bg4a1bg8b6dgb36b3b174d67": ["I don't feel lucky.", "7eda738e-8a85-4975-a1e1-1b3b2c4d641c", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "671fe6f6-6b34-2f5f-4468-777f0f7cab9f"], "h5f626d45g7f23g4202g914agaf80b8f56eec": ["The rest of our crew's half-digested, and you're still alive. That's lucky.", "fd9b4edd-7828-4e22-85a9-ead2ba9d29e4", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentShipment_AD_BetweenAgents.html", "25dd996d-1b40-49ff-ae62-1c4e62482443"]}